{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a0377af5bd","title":"聂荣臻与国防科委所属各院校座谈纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"24062cf5f0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":4,"articleId":"a0377af5bd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"潘复生","id":"004a69d4c7","type":"人物"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"罗瑞卿","id":"6c3c62f283","type":"人物"},{"name":"霍士廉","id":"8b1d13e2f2","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"许世友","id":"c2f8307fbd","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"聂荣臻","id":"d009250878","type":"人物"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f40059ecfa","name":"聂荣臻"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"129a4ca429","type":"title","text":"聂荣臻与国防科委所属各院校座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94236fb3d8","type":"paragraph","text":"〖开始，介绍代表。聂荣臻同志首先听取各院校代表反映情况。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f419d63cf","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到北京工业学院情况时）","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40e3d31087","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“大方向一致的，都要联合起来。”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b042fb26b","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到成都电讯工程学院、西安都电讯工程学院时，介绍了成电两派情况。）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c3471d5da","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“现在四川省混乱得很，有的部队有坏人，不能一样看待。有时部队弄不清楚，支持错了，因此，要求地方部队要了解情况。”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86990447a5","type":"paragraph","text":"（又问了一下交大的情况）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea91cabea6","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“交大两个组织观点一致，怎么不能合并呢？”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5168928b0","type":"paragraph","text":"（交大回答：家里已合并）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"305afbc2be","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“交大夺权了吗？”","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3229531ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（交大回答：以前是“红革会”夺权，现在“红革会”与其他革命造反派矛盾很大，“红革会”犯了机会主义路线错误，大国沙文主义。）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5233ab8d52","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“怎么犯大国沙文主义？”","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12e95dc450","type":"paragraph","text":"（交大回答：他们是较大的组织，他们到处插手，控制《解放日报》提出打倒托派，加剧造反派之间的矛盾，炮打张春桥，针对中央文革。）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c30feadbab","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“他们是多大的组织？斗争是有反复的。上海交通恢复了吗？生产怎么样？学校夺权如何？”","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e3aecf353","type":"paragraph","text":"（交大谈了一下上海的情况，下面问到南航情况，南航代表谈了一些南航的情况。）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1f8d190d7","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“中央反对山头主义。”","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c71b88480","type":"paragraph","text":"（南航谈到：……）","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d97f582fbb","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“我不是保守，开除党籍慢一些，不要被事务性工作冲淡政治工作。”","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd56f19626","type":"paragraph","text":"（有人谈到：他也要夺，你也要夺。）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a2f3f670a","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“联合起来嘛！哪有一个人夺的呢？”","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7fc734a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到军事院校的军官如何打人等）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d5846f210","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“越是军官，越是不听话。”","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7f461c360","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到哈军工问题）","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d45ab0c6fb","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“‘八·八’和‘红旗军’搞到一块，你们主要是争取他们中的群众，要把受蒙蔽的群众 和 他们的头头分开。主要要做他们群众的工作，不要歧视他们。”","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7cf7d8b60e","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“你们应该站在潘复生的一边。”","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a02a8ef79a","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们谈：潘复生应该站在我们一边。）","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3968cd9a8c","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“一样嘛！潘在省委是受排斥的，李范五和一些人排斥他嘛！你们支持他嘛！”“哈市在开始时很乱，我们也很担心。你们哈市没有其他组织吗？”","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc9d4f00e8","type":"paragraph","text":"（哈军工：没有其他组织了。西工大谈了一些情况，说：科委支持保守派。）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52cf16e25c","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“我们没有支持临委会，我们来查一查。”","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"125e0c4b59","type":"paragraph","text":"（西工大：昨天付德林还说支持多数派。）","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a3668ff165","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“少数多数还要看谁是正确的。总是会有变化的。革命派总是由少数变成多数。”","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0dc461f7a4","type":"paragraph","text":"“西安的问题比较复杂，比较混乱。你们对霍士廉的看法怎样？”","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"501cec0f45","type":"paragraph","text":"（答：省委和西北局有矛盾。）","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8c19eb047","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“在军队一样么！霍在抗战时在山东。《红旗》十三期社论指的清楚。我没有和霍在一块工作过。不太了解。”","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86680cb832","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学说：李世英不是真革命，否则为什么自杀？）","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f00cd0685d","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“陈总谈他原来受过害，对他有同情心，但希望在内部，夺权怎么样？解放军参加了吗？”","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfd9f9f4b5","type":"paragraph","text":"（西工大：没有反复，解放军支持了我们。）","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88d59f2f25","type":"paragraph","text":"（哈工大：目前哈市的运动情况有所变化，我们有些情况请示聂总，谈军委八条命令，给答复。）","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bba74b392","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“可以派少数搞科委问题。”","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4828299534","type":"paragraph","text":"（哈工大：科委的会议我们是否可以参加？）","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"158de238cd","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“公开的可以参加。我的意见是科委商讨一下，可以找几个单位商讨一下，有意见交换一下。”","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f814e4b18f","type":"paragraph","text":"“关于毕业生分配，肯定也有争论，现在也没有决定，我的意见是实事求是。（因为有的学生家庭有困难）还可以讨论。”","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba9cb97233","type":"paragraph","text":"“关于经济主义，已经批了就算了，不要再追。”","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"536d438a46","type":"paragraph","text":"（北航谈了一下夺权问题。聂又问了太机情况，南京炮工情况。谈到西军临委会时）","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a6965ed17","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：“不是和稀泥，对于筹委会的人一定要区别对待，应该给予他们教育。帮助他们成为新人。”（谈到科委内部和院校串联问题。）","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da93d66941","type":"paragraph","text":"\"我们和你们是工作关系，不是什么串联，对于黑帮儿子，我们还要教育。父亲是黑帮，儿子不一定是黑帮。自来红思想是不对的。应该改造。应该教育，分配工作。可以提意见，（谈到材料问题。）关于材料问题，我们发给你们，（指八条命令以前）八条以后不能发。要同等待遇。现在解放军已介入，地方的问题也很复杂。为什么有的地方夺权成功一点，有的还不成功。现在情况很复杂，蒋介石在台湾。苏修打留学生跟法西斯一样，我们要战备。新疆也很复杂。我们一方面要支持夺权，另一方面要搞战备。养兵千日用在一时。我们一点不能忽视。所以军队上的要分批分期搞。支持左派问题上也很复杂，不能支持错的，在公安系统也要夺权，罗在公安部搞了好几年，我们也不放心。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bb6e613f8","type":"paragraph","text":"在座谈中，聂荣臻同志指示纪要如下：","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9b8007f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、目前军队所处的地位很重要，解放军不仅要支持左派，而且还要做工作，因为派别很多，看不清楚，有时也会弄错了。","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0be11fa0b6","type":"paragraph","text":"二、解放军一方面要支持左派，另一方面要加强战备，一点也不能疏忽。苏修对我们不断挑衅，新疆很乱，我们要提高警惕，因此，军事机关要分期分批搞文化大革命。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04c35694a7","type":"paragraph","text":"三、公安系统在罗瑞卿手下管了十几年，我们对公安系统还不信任，你们夺权，我是支持的。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e49368280","type":"paragraph","text":"四、部队不能夺权。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e85318e201","type":"paragraph","text":"五、要发展根据地，进行大联合，消灭山头主义，联合起来力量才大，要在大方向一致的前提下大联合，统一在毛泽东思想伟大旗帜下。","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dca5a40478","type":"paragraph","text":"六、夺权以后，还让原来那些人干（个别除外），你们只起监督作用，不要忙于事务工作。","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff56522892","type":"paragraph","text":"七、夺权以后，在改的时候，你们可以成立一个管理委员会，设立校务部，教务部。选出主任，采取集体领导，至于校长，不一定要了。","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c628c01c2d","type":"paragraph","text":"八、你们搞科委，是可以留一部分人的。不受军委命令的限制。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3675c7d13","type":"paragraph","text":"九、有些干部站在左派方面，你们要欢迎，因为你们不了解的情况，他们是可能了解的。","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84c07a4ffc","type":"paragraph","text":"十、对于黑帮子女，一般不要清理，应该进行教育。争取一个算一个，看他是否与家庭划清界限，考虑将来分配工作。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88ebcb9277","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、原毕业分配方案，可以重新分配，要群众重新讨论研究，对保守派也应分配，但要进行教育。","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"396e656982","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、许世友是一个老干部，人是好的，经过长征。只是性格有些特别。他是站在毛主席这一边的。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09c000af9b","type":"paragraph","text":"十三、红旗军是一个反动的组织，发展相当快，你们要多注意一些。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a0377af5bd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}